{"tid":802621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港勁揪！復仇戰破日本 男子7欖奪金","createTime":"2018-09-01T14:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T16:22:08.000Z","uid":178187,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ac80fd8ef99ea230282e73ef2c6061ae6787993a","tid":802621,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:50:51.000Z","msg":"香港男子七人欖球隊揚威雅加達！連續兩屆於亞運屈居日本隊之下的港隊一破夙命，今晚於決賽以14:0力壓日本隊，摘下港隊今屆亞運第八面金牌，追平港隊2010年奪八金歷來的最佳成績。<br />\n<br />\n港隊傍晚於四強以19:7擊敗南韓闖決賽，今日面對宿敵，港隊開賽氣勢如虹，先有姚錦成達陣，港隊踢入加罰；臨完半場再有虎拿當尼達陣，港隊再入加罰，半場領前14:0。下半場日本隊未有進帳，港隊成功雪恨！<br />\n<br />\n此外，香港女子隊於名次賽以45:0挫新加坡，最終排名第五。香港代表團於2010年廣州亞運奪八金，為歷來最佳；今次七欖封王，把港隊今屆獎牌數改寫成8金18銀19銅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180901/58634677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58634677&d=j098dpu5mEPmWltjgCn2M8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=29226726\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58634677&h=80a5e98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180901/58634677</a>"},{"pid":"1203f08170c3e74994889354bb2dc5769762f8cd","tid":802621,"uid":178187,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"香港隊勁揪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c762b401f34b193394eb0354a0a7981d9ea435d1","tid":802621,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"姚錦成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n今晚又要打J啦"},{"pid":"238827ae22dc40e93596035c93462828b63dc16a","tid":802621,"uid":178187,"like":8,